About Rockland Luggage Since its inception in 1998, Rockland by Fox Luggage has been proudly producing quality luggage and bags for the style savvy traveler. Recognized for its graphic and colorful designs, Rockland prides itself on creating products influenced by current trends in design and fashion. Our products turn heads in a crowd and stand out in the baggage carousel, making it easy for quick exits out the airport. Affordable and travel resistant, Rockland bags are an ideal companion for everything from quick trips to the gym to overnight getaways to extended vacations. Our selection includes: luggage sets (4 piece, 3 piece or 2 piece), hard cases, soft cases, carry ons, rolling backpacks, travel duffels, rolling duffels, cosmetic bags, and kids' backpacks. Over the years, a few Rockland products have been featured in film and television. Their colorful designs make them ideal for an eye catching visual element on screen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 11, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I just bought 3 of these little "rollers", as you can see! Pink and blue for my 7 and 10 year old granddaughters and the beige for myself. I absolutely LOVE them, however...here comes my "rant"! They came in a plastic bag that was secured in a taped up box which I thought was very good protection, uh, not so much! There is a stupid, and I mean STUPID "plastic protective film" on them that literally took me over 20 minutes EACH to peel off! Sure, there's a corner at the top front that says, Peel here, or something like that, but as you're peeling it, matter how slow or careful you are, it tears comes off in smaller pieces which makes it FRUSTRATING and RIDICULOUS! I always read reviews before I purchase here and I did read a few about the plastic film but I thought maybe people were exaggerating, but, no, I was wrong and I AGREE!! All-in-all, I still love these little rollers and I know my granddaughters will as well!!
